{
  "texts": [
    "Due to the fact that all factors have an impact on the final result, it is also crucial to select the other aspects when focusing on one aspect.",
    "Limited by resources and efficiency, it is neither necessary nor feasible to exhaust all possibilities.",
    "When not explicitly specified, the LLM uses ChatGPT released in June 2023 to ensure the consistent recommendation quality.",
    "For the design of prompts, we refer to the template in [44] and emphasize the most recently interacted items to re-rank 20 candidate items.",
    "The default method for modeling user interest is to concatenate the title sequence of recently interacted items using natural languages."
  ]
}